title: Implement Aliasing and Renaming. Closes #50
message:
Implement Aliasing and Renaming. Closes #50
Offers an option to change the displayed label.
An override label is used to achieve this, the original
label is kept and also gets updated if it changes.
An entry can be reset to use the original label again.
There is also an option to add aliases.
In this case a modified copy of the entry is created.
Due to the nature of hashes aliases get identified
by their labelMode and then handled accordingly.

title: Add CATEGORY_LAUNCHER to intent when starting an app
message:
Add CATEGORY_LAUNCHER to intent when starting an app
Without adding this category in some cases the referenced
activity might be recreated and placed on top of the current
back stack. Then the user needs to press the back button to
get to the last used activity. After adding this category the
last used activity is brought to front automatically.

title: Implements #62 and #59
message:
Implements #62 and #59
When one longtaps on an icon, it shows applicable show/hide/pin
entries for each application. An additional configuration parameter
for showing the hidden entries was added so that way. The pin comparator
is also used to shuffle "hidden" entries to the back if the user wants
to see hidden entries. For now, unsorted mode doesn't consider pinning.

title: Pre-cache icons at app start in sperate thread.
message:
Pre-cache icons at app start in sperate thread.

Instead of different threads for each icon, there is now only one extra
thread to load all icon images at once in the background.
This will reduce lags and displaying wrong images when scrolling at 'warp' speed.
